<p>Work as an independent filmmaker, or as a freelancer in directing, producing, screenwriting, editing, cinematography, sound design or recording. Films made by Image Arts graduates have played at major festivals around the world.</p> 
<p>Explore support positions in production management, sound, camera, assistant direction and art departments.</p> 
<p>Engage in advanced studies through a graduate program in film or a related field.</p>
    





